    API Changes:
        - None.

    New Features:
        - None.

    Enhancements:
        - Handle partially indexed files better on post-commit
        - Distribution name change to App-githook-perltidy.
        - First release to CPAN (mostly for the tester reports)

    Bug Fixes:
        - None.

